{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"BatteryManager（电源管理）","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BatteryManager","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BatteryManager\"><code>BatteryManager</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BatteryManager/charging\"><code>charging</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/BatteryManager/chargingTime\"><code>chargingTime</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/BatteryManager/dischargingTime\"><code>dischargingTime</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/BatteryManager/level\"><code>level</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Events</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/BatteryManager/chargingchange_event\"><code>chargingchange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/BatteryManager/chargingtimechange_event\"><code>chargingtimechange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/BatteryManager/dischargingtimechange_event\"><code>dischargingtimechange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/BatteryManager/levelchange_event\"><code>levelchange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>BatteryManager 接口提供方法获取系统电量。&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Navigator/getBattery\"><code>navigator.getBattery</code></a> 方法返回一个 promise 对象，该 promise 将提供一个 BatteryManager 接口，你可以从<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Battery_Status_API\">Battery Status API</a>&nbsp;查询到相关信息。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"batterymanager.charging\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BatteryManager/charging\"><code>BatteryManager.charging</code></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>一个布尔值，说明当前电池是否正在充电。</dd>\n <dt id=\"batterymanager.chargingtime_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/BatteryManager/chargingTime\"><code>BatteryManager.chargingTime</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>一个数字，代表距离充电完毕还需多少秒，如果为 0 则充电完毕。</dd>\n <dt id=\"batterymanager.dischargingtime_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/BatteryManager/dischargingTime\"><code>BatteryManager.dischargingTime</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>一个数字，代表距离电池耗电至空且挂起需要多少秒。</dd>\n <dt id=\"batterymanager.level_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/BatteryManager/level\"><code>BatteryManager.level</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>一个数字，代表电量的放大等级，这个值在 0.0 至 1.0&nbsp;之间。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"事件处理器","title":"事件处理器","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"batterymanager.onchargingchange_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/BatteryManager/chargingchange_event\"><code>BatteryManager.onchargingchange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Reference/Events/chargingchange\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">chargingchange</a></code>事件处理器；电池充电状态更新时被调用。</dd>\n <dt id=\"batterymanager.onchargingtimechange_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/BatteryManager/chargingtimechange_event\"><code>BatteryManager.onchargingtimechange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Reference/Events/chargingtimechange\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">chargingtimechange</a></code>事件处理器；电池充电时间更新时被调用。</dd>\n <dt id=\"batterymanager.ondischargingtimechange_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/BatteryManager/dischargingtimechange_event\"><code>BatteryManager.ondischargingtimechange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Reference/Events/dischargingtimechange\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">dischargingtimechange</a></code>事件处理器；电池断开充电时间更新时被调用。</dd>\n <dt id=\"batterymanager.onlevelchange_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/BatteryManager/levelchange_event\"><code>BatteryManager.onlevelchange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Reference/Events/levelchange\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">levelchange</a></code>事件处理器；电池电量更新时被调用。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"方法","title":"方法","isH3":false,"content":"<p>继承自<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a>:</p>\n\n<p></p><dl>\n <dt id=\"eventtarget.addeventlistener\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\"><code>EventTarget.addEventListener()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>在 EventTarget 上注册特定事件类型的事件处理程序。</dd>\n <dt id=\"eventtarget.removeeventlistener\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/removeEventListener\"><code>EventTarget.removeEventListener()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>EventTarget 中删除事件侦听器。</dd>\n <dt id=\"eventtarget.dispatchevent\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/dispatchEvent\"><code>EventTarget.dispatchEvent()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>将事件分派到此 EventTarget。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"mozilla_chrome_代码的其他方法","title":"Mozilla chrome 代码的其他方法","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Mozilla 扩展，供 JS 实现的事件目标使用以 实现 on* 属性。另见&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/WebIDL_bindings\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">WebIDL bindings</a>&nbsp;绑定。</p><ul>\n <li>void&nbsp;<strong>setEventHandler</strong>(DOMString type, EventHandler handler) <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></li>\n <li>EventHandler&nbsp;<strong>getEventHandler</strong>(DOMString type) <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></li>\n</ul><p></p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/battery/#the-batterymanager-interface","title":"Battery Status API"}],"query":"api.BatteryManager"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.BatteryManager","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BatteryManager/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"其他","title":"其他","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>The <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Battery_Status_API\">电池状态 API</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Navigator/getBattery\"><code>navigator.getBattery</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"方法","id":"方法"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"其他","id":"其他"}],"summary":"BatteryManager 接口提供方法获取系统电量。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"BatteryManager","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"BatteryManager","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"BatteryManager","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"BatteryManager","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"BatteryManager","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"BatteryManager","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/batterymanager","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/batterymanager/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BatteryManager","title":"BatteryManager（电源管理）"}],"pageTitle":"BatteryManager（电源管理） - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}